title: The Peter Schiff Show - 2012 Mar 06 TU [sebaygo1]
description:

The Peter Schiff Show
Tuesday, 06 March 2012


[sebaygo1]


Tom Woods is guest hosting today's show.

Today's first guest is Daniel McCarthy, editor of the American Conservative, on Putin the Permanent; Barack and Bibi; and the Limbaugh "slut" saga.

Today's second guest is Brion McClanahan, author of The Politically Incorrect Guide to the Founding Fathers as well as The Politically Incorrect Guide to Real American Heroes, on his new book, The Founding Fathers Guide to the Constitution.
